Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm... going to die?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.73,0:00:09.98,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The Oracle cells have acclimated\Nto your body and will continue to spread,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,eventually consuming you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you continue to use your God Arc,{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.16,0:00:19.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt that your\Ncompatibility rate will accelerate.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.50,0:00:24.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What if I stopped using my God Arc?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.25,0:00:27.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'd give you another\Nthree years to live at most.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.30,0:00:33.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you can't\Nstave off the inevitable.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.42,0:00:37.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,My advice is to retire as a God Eater\Nto give yourself more time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.89,0:00:41.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Though, even if you do,\Nwe'll have to continue regulating your Bias Factor.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.68,0:00:43.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,My Bias Factor?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.64,0:00:48.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Like any Aragami, the Oracle cells\Nin your body have a bias inclination.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.23,0:00:54.24,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If left unchecked,\Nthey'll run rampant, and you will die.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.78,0:00:58.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Since you've become a God Eater,\Nyou can no longer leave Fenrir.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.83,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you still want to fight\Nknowing this, however...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will restore your God Arc.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's your call.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.75,0:01:11.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Who else knows about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.01,0:01:14.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Only Licca and myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to think about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a huge step forward for mankind.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.85,0:01:27.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no sign of rejection at all.\NHis compatibility rate is stunning.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.98,0:01:30.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hybrid of man and Aragami...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.23,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By analyzing this child's compatibility...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.78,0:01:37.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we'll be able to engineer humans\Nthat can stand up to the Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.16,0:01:38.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A God Eater, you might say...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.20,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look at this reaction!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a monster...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's a rat in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Send for a cat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.70,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The giant protrusions around the world,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.82,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,which were causing damage on a global scale,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,have stopped as mysteriously as they began.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,The U.N. is directing all available resources\Ntowards rescue and reconstruction.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,However, the unknown lifeforms\Nthat have appeared since,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.96,0:02:38.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,dubbed "the menace of the gods" or "Aragami",
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,have proven impervious to every weapon\Nused against them, and casualties are—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,If we had reported this sooner...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,Johannes...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,You're right. Maybe we could have\Nreduced the number of casualties.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.61,0:02:57.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,Paylor!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,Don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.95,0:03:05.12,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Amidst the darkness,\Nonly those marks emit light.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That light...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.17,0:03:17.00,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You don't think the higher-ups\Nused that technology...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.00,0:03:20.22,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's call it the Bias Factor.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Those protrusions sure are picky eaters.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Fenrir\Nanticipated this happening?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.77,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It makes you wonder.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Paylor...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.77,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think the Bias Factor\Ncan be weaponized?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say for sure\Nwithout running more tests.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.15,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Johannes?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Drastic times call for drastic measures.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.45,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We're resuming our research.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Humanity will need weapons\Nto fight the Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You are all here today
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.63,0:04:01.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,for the installation of the guiding device\Nthat is the keystone of Operation Meteorite.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.68,0:04:06.22,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The work will be done by a special\Ntech team, but there will be risks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Your mission is to protect them.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.60,0:04:16.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There are five devices,\Nso you will be divided into five units.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.23,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Those who will lead\Nthe units are as follows:
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Sakuya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.82,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oomori Tatsumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Brendan Bardell.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Gina Dickinson.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.24,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Utsugi Lenka.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Lenka... is in charge?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a unit leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But I don't have a God Arc...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I won't stop you if you choose to drop out.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.30,0:04:50.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is a critical mission for Aegis.\NIs it too difficult for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.14,0:04:50.97,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Aegis...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.52,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No. My apologies.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I gladly accept.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Good. With that...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.82,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, you'll be in Utsugi's unit.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.40,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma... sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Forget the formalities.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Watch your back around the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,"Grim Reaper"?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.64,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Have you made your decision yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.98,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I... just wanted to help...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.65,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If nothing else, it can serve as a shield.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.28,0:05:47.53,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,As I explained earlier, using your God Arc\Nwill affect your life expectancy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.20,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you can't accept that, resign now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.78,0:05:55.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you're teamed up with Soma,\Nyou might not need to use it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,About Soma...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,People keep calling him the "Grim Reaper".
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,"Grim Reaper"?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Fate is cruel.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.88,0:06:12.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It would be fair to say\Nthat both of you are victims of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.02,0:06:17.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to know more,\Nlook him up in the database.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You can decide what\Nto think of him after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.45,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Schicksal...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.84,0:06:48.72,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It was working on them before!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.85,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Pull back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The reports say it stopped working again.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No doubt the Aragami's\Nbias inclination has changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.61,0:07:11.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,So the Aragami are evolving...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I told them it was too soon\Nfor practical application!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But we have proven that it works.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We've already saved so many.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.25,0:07:24.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm worried about claiming\Nthat it'll solve all our problems.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.34,0:07:29.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Three more Eastern European nations\Nhave agreed to use Fenrir's technology.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This makes over 50 nations\Nto sign contracts with Fenrir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.22,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to what\Nexisting weaponry can do.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If we perfect the\NBias Factor in our weapons...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.39,0:07:46.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That Bias Factor will degrade the moment\Nit's extracted from the Oracle cells.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Did you design this?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.53,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.53,0:08:00.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's the only way a refined\NBias Factor will work in weapons.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But this isn't a conventional weapon...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a living weapon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A morbid yet brilliant idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.80,0:08:13.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We can cultivate Oracle cells ourselves\Nto create artificial Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.35,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However, there's one problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.68,0:08:23.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If it's made up of Oracle cells,\Nit'll devour anything it touches.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.40,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Can't it be controlled remotely?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a living being and as such,\Nwould be hard to control.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Analyzing it would be a long process.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.70,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There is one possibility...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.16,0:08:45.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We could inject the Bias Factor into\Na human and let their body adapt to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed, that would be\Nthe most effective method.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But to do something so hellish...{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.18,0:08:59.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We'd need an incredible amount\Nof volunteers to test it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.56,0:09:06.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Administering it via the womb could\Nmake adaptation far safer than a direct dosage.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.48,0:09:11.11,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe so, but who would\Npossibly agree to it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.90,0:09:18.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Or should I say that {\i1}we{\i0} will.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.59,0:09:38.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I hear you're going on the mission\Nwith the New-Type.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's an important device, so don't break it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.11,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Rindou.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.11,0:09:58.11,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Quit staring off into space.\NI've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I just wanted a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.99,0:10:06.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you around either.\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.16,0:10:10.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know, I was on a date.\NNothing special.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A ladies' man, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.85,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You and Soma have a mission?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If left to his own devices,\Nhe'd go out there to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.06,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.85,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,So we need to place these stakes\Naround the guiding device?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Once activated,\Na mock defense wall will be formed.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.67,0:10:57.26,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,And until the operation starts,\Nthe devices will be safe from the Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,This technology is still being refined, however.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.51,0:11:04.35,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,We won't know how durable it is until it's tested.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.93,0:11:06.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.22,0:11:11.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,Major Amamiya, the new recruits\Nwill begin training at 1200 hours.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,Understood. I'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,That's it for explanations.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.32,0:11:21.49,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,The guiding devices are vital.\NYou know what to do, Utsugi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.70,GJM_Main,,0,0,100,,Um... Major Amamiya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.20,0:11:28.83,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,620,640,680,1550,2050)}Why did you step down as a God Eater?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.66,0:11:34.46,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen an Aragami being born?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.00,0:11:36.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you did, you'd think the same...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.34,0:11:44.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That Aragami cannot be exterminated.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.35,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.56,0:11:52.35,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I have faith that some day this will all end.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.98,0:11:58.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,So I chose to nurture the next generation\Nand entrust the future to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.07,0:11:59.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The future...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You'll understand in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.83,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm told the guiding devices are invaluable.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If we fail, the completion of Aegis will be delayed.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's work together to make this a success.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Not really, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a little nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.43,0:12:32.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,People who go out with Soma...\Ndon't come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's just a rumor, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.27,0:12:35.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.02,0:12:40.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die,\Nthen stay away from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.61,0:12:49.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If worse comes to worst,\Nforget the device and run.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The guiding devices have been set up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.76,0:13:08.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Get on with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.47,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Objective complete. Let's head back.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.18,0:13:51.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.11,0:14:02.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,An Aragami?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(3158,0,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Have you ever seen an Aragami being born?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,They came right out of the ground...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aragami cannot be exterminated.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.63,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The wall!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad! What do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.90,0:14:46.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Come at me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.46,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Is he going to protect the guiding device?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.63,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Bring the copter down!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.80,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Retrieving the guiding device!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.80,0:15:14.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's over for us if the wall is destroyed\Nwhile we try to salvage the device!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you even able to\Nprotect us with your God Arc?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You guys stay on board.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.98,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You'll only be in the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Leave the device!\NYou can't take all of them on!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A monster.{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of his partners die...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.97,0:15:53.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An unholy child who killed\Nhis mother to be born.{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.97,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If anyone dies, it'll be me.{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.65,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're pregnant?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Johannes!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Considering the situation...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.41,0:16:18.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Paylor's idea is the best possible choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.00,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,As a fellow researcher,\NI would be the ideal candidate.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.63,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But if this should fail...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You... and our baby...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's got to be another way!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's keep thinking!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.93,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I agree with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.64,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, we don't have to decide now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.27,0:16:45.15,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's no time left for mankind...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.94,0:16:49.65,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me, Johannes, Paylor.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,to give hope to my baby\Nand to the future humanity.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.04,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Position the copter above the device!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Utsugi?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Disconnect the device!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, attack like you did\Nbefore and kill them all!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's no time to reposition...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.83,0:17:48.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't kill your mother to be born!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.84,0:17:50.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.59,0:17:56.55,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You were entrusted with hope.\NHope that your mother passed on to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.55,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't see the Grim Reaper in you, so shoot!{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.00,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.13,0:18:32.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You're not a Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.46,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Utsugi...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Utsugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to the device?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You looked me up in the database, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You think you know what kind of person I am?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.70,0:19:09.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe not, but I think I understand a little now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.37,0:19:14.38,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Because I have people who make life worth living.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.25,0:19:19.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why'd you accept the mission in your condition?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.26,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,In order to complete Aegis.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What good is completing something like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You can't destroy Aragami\Nunless you destroy their cores.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,And even if you destroy their cores,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.27,0:19:39.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,the scattered Oracle cells will amass again\Nand give birth to more Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.20,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a cycle of despair.{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.74,0:19:46.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Then pass it on to someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The same way your mother did.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.79,0:19:55.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You can't die until you connect\Nyour life to someone else's.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.97,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't die,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,so you don't get to die either.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.32,0:20:22.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Like the Indian legend?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.45,0:20:26.24,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Do you not like it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.24,0:20:31.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A nectar of the gods that bestows\Nthe force of life to mankind...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.29,0:20:37.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I believe that it's something humanity needs now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.79,0:20:38.80,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a fine name.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.38,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.01,0:20:46.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We can't wait to see you, Soma.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A dam?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.86,0:21:02.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... It was surrounded by a forest\Nand there were people...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.11,0:21:08.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Amamiya Rindou seems to have\Nsome association with these people.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.95,0:21:09.83,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.66,0:21:14.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone seemed quite close.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.83,0:21:20.46,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't heed my warning.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.80,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,And you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.38,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Then you'll retire—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please fix it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please fix my God Arc.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.65,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell anyone about my condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You certainly are fascinating, boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.04,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Very well then. I'll restore your God Arc.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.92,0:21:57.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.43,0:22:10.35,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Is this the thing that's calling out to them?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.26,0:22:16.23,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is the Aragami that devoured\Nyour mother and father.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.77,0:22:19.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Mother... Father...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.02,0:22:24.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. You can fight now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.99,0:22:29.11,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me what I taught you.\NYou can pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.03,0:22:33.24,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You... taught me...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.83,0:22:35.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.96,0:22:37.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.08,0:22:42.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.09,0:22:44.80,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.46,0:22:47.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is your enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,An Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.18,0:22:56.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.43,0:22:59.85,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that... this is a God Arc?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.56,0:23:04.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I designed this with his compatibility rate in mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.53,0:23:08.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Aisha...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.57,0:23:12.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The hope for the future which you entrusted...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.87,0:23:16.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone get in the way of it.
Comment: 10,0:23:24.67,0:23:24.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Lemme rest a bit.{ep12, 17:51}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.96,0:23:27.67,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,Rindou!{ep12, 09:05}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.67,0:23:28.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?{ep11, 19:52}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} will destroy...{ep11, 07:56}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.01,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,Get out there, Utsugi!{ep11, 20:55}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.64,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm entrusting this God Arc to you!{ep12, 04:03}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.68,0:23:32.64,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,My family...{ep11, 11:10}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.64,0:23:33.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Only darkness.{ep12, 19:52}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.76,0:23:35.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Can humanity rise to become gods?{doesn't exist, thanks ufotable}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.68,0:23:36.97,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We'll turn this around!{ep13, 05:39}
